{"tid":446471,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［疑難雜症］ 在汀九橋爆胎求意見","createTime":"2017-10-24T10:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T04:24:55.000Z","uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"788da70664157d800657f3c4c3edd34c24e84af0","tid":446471,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"出汀九時後胎爆左，現在人車安全亦將車泊左在一個咪標停車場（如要繼續行駛需換後備胎）<br />\n<br />\n問題來了，要換胎要捱到翻屯門，但怕後備胎捱唔到翻去（怕有危險）<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲想問問意見：<br />\n<br />\n1. 你會否自行換後備胎捱到翻屯門？（點都有一段要行公路，諗過深井落下路慢轆）<br />\n<br />\n2. 叫拖車  （但費用未知）   <br />\n<br />\n3. 想問問有無平價拖車推介<br />\n<br />\n希望各巴絲解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fdfd0fecb243b745a41d36ad1b538df79c8031","tid":446471,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"入到去係咪即刻有車房幫你搞先"},{"pid":"4dcd6fc2b1352ad852f14209f50b3af0b8c9bd41","tid":446471,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"我只係怕後轆換左後備胎   未必捱到翻屯門     就算落下路都有段要行翻公路去深井  <br />\n<br />\n但報個價加轆仔都要800-900<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868ab0f8cacecdd298d9a24d0641b4fff937e5e1","tid":446471,"uid":49461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:17:53.000Z","msg":"如果 爆一條<br />\n緊係 自己換完之後 揸去補胎啦"},{"pid":"f61ada0a827f33d77504b81f09386df5db46fe77","tid":446471,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:36:19.000Z","msg":"行公路你都可以慢車嫁"},{"pid":"d0629747a238cfc89cc1ed2872d4739e09103599","tid":446471,"uid":68516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:49:27.000Z","msg":"梗係換呔，到呔舖補喇<br />\n士啤呔好多只係可以行7-80<br />\n<br />\n樓主你真係怕危險定係唔識換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de6be74ffb70413db58ec3e50df64c0ef06311d","tid":446471,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只係怕後轆換左後備胎   未必捱到翻屯門     就算落下路都有段要行翻公路去深井  <br />\n<br />\n但報個價加轆仔都要800-900<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解捱唔到？？？<br />\n裝咗士啤呔一般建議你揸慢啲，咁就冇問題"},{"pid":"41f7b37ec08510e025107ec0e57d49fc98e63b47","tid":446471,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"汀九行下路慢慢返屯門咪得囉"},{"pid":"46305ead13a2d4689b15686989b9350916e7a162","tid":446471,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係換呔，到呔舖補喇<br />\n士啤呔好多只係可以行7-80<br />\n<br />\n樓主你真係怕危險定係唔識換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識換  上早兩個月先換左對全新頭轆p zero <br />\n<br />\n點知依家到後轆    我睇過應該唔會就咁爆胎   氣嘴位有問題<br />\n<br />\n如果捱到，出翻汀九果條路我應該點置理？   需要打住死火燈行 定  慢車60-70<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4644cec38bb1106feec3446cc4f9b1e94a5336","tid":446471,"uid":54066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:01:20.000Z","msg":"您條備用輪廢架？ <br />\n<br />\n梗係1. 捱到返屋企， 揾日出鋪頭換番咪得"},{"pid":"7b75d8fac8f13a275b99598f08796e067fcc51e5","tid":446471,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>梗係換呔，到呔舖補喇<br />\n士啤呔好多只係可以行7-80<br />\n<br />\n樓主你真係怕危險定係唔識換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識換  上早兩個月先換左對全新頭轆p zero <br />\n<br />\n點知依家到後轆    我睇過應該唔會就咁爆胎   氣嘴位有問題<br />\n<br />\n如果捱到，出翻汀九果條路我應該點置理？   需要打住死火燈行 定  慢車60-70<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好就慢少少喇  士啤呔又未去到咁廢"},{"pid":"7b1890e9d2e64f4fcc2a7aead3a15c1838aaa936","tid":446471,"uid":113749,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"捱到返去啦<br />\n你條後備胎紙做架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd1014fbdd16389b8628567ab3612b2058569de","tid":446471,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>梗係換呔，到呔舖補喇<br />\n士啤呔好多只係可以行7-80<br />\n<br />\n樓主你真係怕危險定係唔識換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識換  上早兩個月先換左對全新頭轆p zero <br />\n<br />\n點知依家到後轆    我睇過應該唔會就咁爆胎   氣嘴位有問題<br />\n<br />\n如果捱到，出翻汀九果條路我應該點置理？   需要打住死火燈行 定  慢車60-70<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好就慢少少喇  士啤呔又未去到咁廢</blockquote><br />\n最緊要上緊啲呔螺絲"},{"pid":"edebdc976609e34d9870560bd7d048e340834837","tid":446471,"uid":63247,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:10:17.000Z","msg":"不如你考慮下賣左架車？"},{"pid":"93ae106da70d7463bb843f245679a7dd467d40fb","tid":446471,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:22:49.000Z","msg":"講到條後備胎紙皮做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起澳洲見過人長期用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a8eecaa3066bd6ad255d831afb50db2a142b51","tid":446471,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到條後備胎紙皮做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起澳洲見過人長期用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳洲好多車係用鐵軨，唔好唔會係後備胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18180bdfe77d1682fc8567ec21be2dc9b0aac834","tid":446471,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>梗係換呔，到呔舖補喇<